name: Jungle Bali ATV
address: Senganan, Kawan, Kec. Penebel, Kabupaten Tabanan, Bali 82191, Indonesia
review 1: Awesome team! We had so much fun, everyone is so friendly and helpful. I was a bit scared, the guys jump on and help the entire way. Great lunch and amazing views!!!!
review 2: Fantastic day. Definitely not what we expected - it was more thrilling than we thought it would be. The tour guides were very friendly and helpful and made the experience really fun. Must do activity for those with a sense of adventure. No prior quad bike experience necessary, the guys will help you along the way. Lunch was great and the scenery beautiful. Well worth the money!
review 3: A challenging experience of driving the quad to around the rice field and the cocoa plantation on small river.
review 4: Had a great time with this company. The staff were really helpful and the route was really fun.  I was expecting it to be much more boring of a trail and was pleasantly surprised that it was a real fun trip. I will be recommending this company to my friends
